355
00:17:07.470 --> 00:17:09.710
Forklar os lidt om
<i>Basil fra Baker Street.</i>


356
00:17:10.550 --> 00:17:12.830
Tja, <i>Basil fra Baker Street</i>
handler om...


357
00:17:13.630 --> 00:17:14.670
en lille mus,

358
00:17:14.990 --> 00:17:17.110
der er ligesom Sherlock Holmes.

359
00:17:17.550 --> 00:17:20.510
<i>En af de første ting,</i>
<i>Roy gjorde, var at arrangere en dag,</i>


360
00:17:20.670 --> 00:17:24.990
<i>hvor vi kunne høre</i>
<i>historien for hele filmen.</i>


361
00:17:25.390 --> 00:17:29.270
